results.summary: Need a gluten free breakfast? Easy Weekday Breakfast Muffins could be an outstanding recipe to try. steps.step: Whisk eggs together in a medium bowl.
Add chopped pepper and onion, salt and pepper, cheese, and milk. Fill muffin tin halfway with egg mixture.
Add a potato tot to each. Top with cheese.
Place in oven for 20 minutes or until fully cooked.
Serve immediately or store for later.
